text: The eleventh season of RuPaul's Drag Race aired on VH1 from February 28, 2019 to May 30, 2019. The cast featured fourteen new queens and one returning queen, making it the largest cast of the series so far, all announced in a live stream hosted by season 10 winner Aquaria and Adam Rippon on January 24, 2019. The winner of the eleventh season of RuPaul's Drag Race was Yvie Oddly, with Brooke Lynn Hytes being the runner-up, and Nina West being Miss Congeniality. Season 10 contestant Vanessa Vanjie Mateo returned to the competition.
